- [ ] Harness compiles and passes its own tests
- [ ] Logging produces readable, parseable output
- [ ] Benchmarks produce accurate statistical results
- [ ] Comparison correctly identifies differences
- [ ] Example test demonstrates full workflow
- [ ] Documentation explains usage patterns

